Class TimeTableServiceSpringImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.co.rays.project0.Service.TimeTableServiceSpringImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeTableServiceInt

    @Service(value="timetableService")
public class TimeTableServiceSpringImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements TimeTableServiceInt
    Session facade of Timetable Service. It is transactional, apply delcarative transactions with help of Spring AOP. If unchecked exception is propagated from a method then transaction will be rolled back. Default propogation value is Propagation.REQUIRED and readOnly = false
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    DAO
